a045b0c34d57eca47f78436d2a872e7b.sql_template: SE{PrenomFr}CT LIBEL{PrenomFr}LOCALITEFR FROM localite WHERE CODEPOSTAL IS NOT NULL AND CODEPOSTAL <> ''

7fc8c3665ac645399146494544841af5.sql_template: SELECT MAX(Solde) AS plus_grand_solde FROM eleve

a25db7af5078fc59c00ce569a7508f90.sql_template:
SELECT DISTINCT inscriptioneleve.Personne 
FROM inscriptioneleve 
WHERE inscriptioneleve.groupe IS NOT NULL

993a819b7904286f09ed9781ef9034c8.sql_template:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS nombre_classes 
FROM classe 
WHERE ID_ANNEE_SCO = (SELECT id FROM anneescolaire WHERE Actif = 1)

70fd9f19003de6e47e372941bf78770a.sql_template: SELECT LIBELLEETABFR FROM etablissement WHERE id = 1

e2a8ac1cbbfdae12d5adf2147cbe419e.sql_template:
SELECT e.id, p.NomFr, p.PrenomFr, i.Date, i.AnneeScolaire 
FROM inscriptioneleve i 
JOIN eleve e ON i.Eleve = e.id 
JOIN personne p ON e.IdPersonne = p.id 
WHERE i.Personne = 161

3c9ab55c5ef5a0a6321249ebfe7c3b02.sql_template:
SELECT e.id, p.NomFr, p.PrenomFr, e.photo 
FROM eleve e 
JOIN personne p ON e.IdPersonne = p.id 
WHERE e.photo IS NOT NULL

3f335e9a7451c72e3f35931c8b27070f.sql_template:
SELECT p.NomFr, p.PrenomFr, c.NOMCLASSEFR 
FROM eleve e 
JOIN personne p ON e.IdPersonne = p.id 
JOIN inscriptioneleve ie ON e.id = ie.Eleve 
JOIN classe c ON ie.Classe = c.id 
WHERE c.CODECLASSEFR = {CODECLASSEFR}
